PrecisRe-appointment of SARAH FITZGERALD of Edmonton, Alberta, as full-time member of the Canada Labour Relations Board to hold office during good behaviour for a term ending on December 31, 1998 or until the dissolution of the Board, whichever is earlier, effective July 5, 1998.

precis:
Re-appointment of SARAH FITZGERALD of Edmonton, Alberta, as full-time
member of the Canada Labour Relations Board to hold office during good
behaviour for a term ending on December 31, 1998 or until the dissolution
of the Board, whichever is earlier, effective July 5, 1998.
